commit.message:
Some form-check fixes and features (#180)

* renderers: Only apply form-check classes to selected labels/inputs

Only labels and inputs found underneath the enclosing radio/checkbox div
should be applied form-check-label and form-check-input classes.
Otherwise we would select every labels on the document, even those who
might not concern the current form.

* renderers: Allow to override the default form-check CSS class

When displaying checkboxes and radio buttons, bootstrap4 allows for two
different rendering options: form-check and form-check-inline.

Add a new form_check_class attribute to both bootstrap_form and
bootstrap_field templatetags. The default value is form-check, but it
can be overridden by anything, e.g.: "form-check form-check-inline".

Some form-check fixes and features (#180)

* renderers: Only apply form-check classes to selected labels/inputs

Only labels and inputs found underneath the enclosing radio/checkbox div
should be applied form-check-label and form-check-input classes.
Otherwise we would select every labels on the document, even those who
might not concern the current form.

* renderers: Allow to override the default form-check CSS class

When displaying checkboxes and radio buttons, bootstrap4 allows for two
different rendering options: form-check and form-check-inline.

Add a new form_check_class attribute to both bootstrap_form and
bootstrap_field templatetags. The default value is form-check, but it
can be overridden by anything, e.g.: "form-check form-check-inline".
